//axhob_operation
{rbtgo_sa_list}

NOTE: This operation lists all service accounts in the
{rbtgi_depot_project}.
It is a multi-role operation that can be invoked by any authenticated role with project read access.

//axhos_step
. *Authenticate*:
.. {rbbc_require}
caller has valid OAuth token with `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform` scope
.. {rbbc_store}
`«ACCESS_TOKEN»` from caller context

//axhos_step
. *List Service Accounts*:
.. {rbbc_call}
link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/list[iam.projects.serviceAccounts.list] with:
... method: `GET`
... endpoint: `https://iam.googleapis.com/v1/projects/{rbrr_depot_project_id}/serviceAccounts`
... header: `Authorization: Bearer «ACCESS_TOKEN»`
.. {rbbc_require}
HTTP 200 response
.. {rbbc_store}
`«ACCOUNTS»` from response `.accounts[]` array
.. {rbbc_store}
`«ACCOUNT_COUNT»` from response `.accounts | length`

//axhos_step
. *Handle Empty Result*:
.. If `«ACCOUNT_COUNT»` is 0:
... {rbbc_show}
"No service accounts found in project"
... Return success

//axhoo_output_of_type
{rbtgi_depot_project}
. *Display Results*:
.. {rbbc_show}
"Found «ACCOUNT_COUNT»` service account(s):"
.. For each account in `«ACCOUNTS»`:
... {rbbc_show}
account `.email` and `.displayName`
.. {rbbc_show}
listing completed successfully

//axhoc_completion
Successful execution lists all service accounts in the depot project.

//axhob_operation
{rbtgo_sa_delete}

NOTE: This operation deletes a service account from the
{rbtgi_depot_project}.
It is a multi-role operation that can be invoked by any authenticated role with IAM admin access.

//axhop_parameter_from_arg
{rbgt_service_account}
. *Validate Input Parameters*:
.. {rbbc_require}
`«INPUT_SA_EMAIL»` provided as first argument
.. {rbbc_fatal}
if missing: "Service account email required"

//axhos_step
. *Authenticate*:
.. {rbbc_require}
caller has valid OAuth token with `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/cloud-platform` scope
.. {rbbc_store}
`«ACCESS_TOKEN»` from caller context

//axhos_step
. *Delete Service Account*:
.. {rbbc_call}
link:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/delete[iam.projects.serviceAccounts.delete] with:
... method: `DELETE`
... endpoint: `https://iam.googleapis.com/v1/projects/{rbrr_depot_project_id}/serviceAccounts/«INPUT_SA_EMAIL»`
... header: `Authorization: Bearer «ACCESS_TOKEN»`
.. {rbbc_require}
HTTP 200 response OR HTTP 404 (already deleted)
.. {rbbc_warn}
if HTTP 404: "Service account not found (already deleted)"

//axhoo_output_of_type
{rbtgi_depot_project}
. *Display Results*:
.. {rbbc_show}
delete operation completed

//axhoc_completion
Successful completion is indicated by the "delete operation completed" message.
